QuestData.Title: The Creeping Carpet of Ihgaluk
QuestData.Description: Ah, roaches! I once bought a pet roach in the Undercity.$b$bRoaches will soak up disease like a sponge, and then spread it as far as they can run. Which is pretty far.$b$bIhgaluk Crag is crawling with the things, and they carry Skumblade filth all over of this island. Crush as many of them as you can while you're there.
